        PUSH: {
          actions: assign({
            queue: ({ context, event }) => context.queue.concat(event.text)
          })
        }
      },
      after: {
        AUTO: [
          { target: 'showing', guard: 'hasNext', reenter: true, actions: 'pull' },
          { target: 'idle', actions: 'clearCurrent' }
        ]
      }
    }
  }
});
```

Add a 'PAUSE_AUTODISMISS' event that freezes the auto-dismiss timer when the user hovers a toast, and a 'RESUME' event to restart the countdown:

